---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Dog Boarding Software" description="Dog boarding software for kennels and overnight stays. Room assignments, multi-night bookings, feeding schedules, and automated deposits.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="badge-primary mb-4">Dog Boarding Software</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Fill More Kennels, Reduce Admin Hassle</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Complete dog boarding and kennel management software for overnight stays, multi-night bookings, room assignments, automated deposits, and add-on services.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">Start Free Trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing/" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">View Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">What Is Dog Boarding Software?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Dog boarding software is a digital management platform designed specifically for pet boarding facilities. It handles overnight stay bookings, room/suite assignments, vaccination tracking, feeding schedules, medication administration, payment processing, and customer communication.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Unlike general booking tools, boarding software understands multi-night stays, capacity management, and the unique needs of overnight pet care.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Key Features</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Multi-Night Booking</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Handle extended stays with automatic pricing calculations and room availability across date ranges.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Room Assignments</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Assign pets to specific rooms or suites with drag-and-drop scheduling and conflict prevention.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Feeding & Medication</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Track feeding schedules, special diets, and medication requirements for each guest.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Vaccination Tracking</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Automated alerts ensure no expired vaccinations slip through. Block bookings for non-compliant pets.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Deposits & Payments</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Collect deposits at booking to reduce no-shows. Process payments securely with saved cards.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Owner Updates</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Send photo updates, feeding logs, and daily reports to reassure pet parents.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">FAQs</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">How much does dog boarding software cost?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Most platforms cost £40-£120/month depending on features and facility size. PetCare.Software starts at £40/month with no setup fees.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Can it handle both boarding and daycare?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. PetCare.Software manages boarding, <a href="/dog-daycare-software/" class="link">daycare</a>, and <a href="/cattery-software/" class="link">cattery</a> services from one login.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">What about peak season management?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Built-in waitlist management, early booking discounts, and capacity alerts help you maximize revenue during busy periods.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-red to-brand-red-dark text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Fill More Kennels?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        See how PetCare.Software helps boarding facilities save time and increase bookings.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn bg-white text-brand-red hover:bg-gray-100 text-lg px-8 py-4">
        Start Your Free Trial
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
